00:01:38.062 --> 00:01:39.624
and we say, okay, is this greater than

00:01:39.624 --> 00:01:40.865
or less than?

00:01:40.865 --> 00:01:42.950
Is this less than five or greater than

00:01:42.950 --> 00:01:44.633
